@startuml 08_LibrarySearch
!theme plain
title Ruffnova - 库搜索与过滤时序图

actor User
participant "AppSidebar" as Sidebar
participant "AppState" as State
participant "SearchService" as SearchSvc
participant "LibraryService" as LibSvc
participant "CollectionService" as CollSvc
participant "LibraryContentView" as Content
participant "LibraryFileCell" as Cell

== 搜索流程 ==

User -> Sidebar : 输入搜索文本
Sidebar -> State : updateSearchText(text)
activate State
State -> State : searchText = text\nisSearching = !text.isEmpty

alt 搜索文本非空
    State -> SearchSvc : search(query: text)
    activate SearchSvc
    SearchSvc -> LibSvc : LibraryService.shared.items
    SearchSvc -> CollSvc : CollectionService.shared

    SearchSvc -> SearchSvc : 过滤匹配:\n1. name (不区分大小写)\n2. url path\n3. tags\n4. notes\n5. collection names\n6. "favorite" → isFavorite\n7. availability status\n8. compatibility status\n9. content type

    SearchSvc --> State : [LibraryItem] results
    deactivate SearchSvc

    State -> Content : 显示搜索结果视图
    Content -> Cell : 渲染匹配的条目
else 搜索文本为空
    State -> Content : 显示正常库视图
end
deactivate State

== 排序与过滤 ==

User -> Content : 选择排序/过滤器
Content -> LibSvc : items(matching: filter, sortedBy: order)
activate LibSvc

LibSvc -> LibSvc : filtered(by: filter)
note right of LibSvc
  过滤器:
  .all, .favorites, .recent,
  .missing, .compatibilityIssues,
  .animation, .interactive,
  .continuePlaying, .recentlyAdded,
  .untagged
end note

LibSvc -> LibSvc : sorted(by: order)
note right of LibSvc
  排序:
  .name (字母序)
  .lastOpened (最近打开)
  .dateAdded (添加时间)
  .fileSize (文件大小)
end note

LibSvc --> Content : [LibraryItem]
deactivate LibSvc

== 多选批量操作 ==

User -> Content : 进入多选模式
Content -> Content : selectedItems: Set<UUID>

User -> Content : 选择多个条目
Content -> Content : toggleSelection(for: id)

User -> Content : 批量操作 (收藏/删除)
Content -> LibSvc : setSelectedFavorites(true/false)
Content -> LibSvc : removeSelectedItems()
LibSvc -> LibSvc : remove items\n清理 thumbnails, bookmarks, collections

@enduml
